author: Warhammer
description:
Congratulations on picking up your War of the Rohirrim – Battle of Edoras box! We bet you’re super excited about the new movie and to bring the world of middle earth to life through warhammer! But before you get your new miniatures onto the gaming table and battle it out, there’s just a few things we’d like to show you first. Ollie & Adam are here to get you through painting this epic box set as quickly as possible so you can deploy it onto the battlefield and face down your opponents with some awesomely painted miniatures! This video is a whistle-stop tour through painting this box set, focusing on the strategy behind tackling such a hefty project. Whether you’re painting the Heroic Rohirrim or the villainous Hill Tribesmen, or maybe even both - we’ve got you covered!
